data.description: Single-level Apple Valley oasis! This beautiful home is 1,945 sq ft, 3 bedrooms, a versatile den, and 2.5 bathrooms. The 12' ceilings in the entry and den lend a grand and airy ambiance. The heart of the home is the kitchen, complete with granite countertops and stainless steel appliances. The adjacent living area provides a comfortable setting for relaxation and entertainment. The property is also equipped with a solar panel system to help you take advantage of renewable energy. Please note that the solar panel system is attached but not paid for. Set on a generous 1.01-acre lot.
